Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================Pre===================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去收集破烂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得很冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我什么也做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在我身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 一直留在我身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为这样 我才必须离开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了两人的生活能永远延续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================OP===================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:21.37,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}熟悉的坡道上 却已不见你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.53,0:01:27.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}柔和的阳光 透过树叶投下斑点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:32.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}我独自一人 伫立在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:39.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}回顾着那些 温暖的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.09,0:01:47.71,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}只有你 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:53.78,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}在变幻的时间中 永驻我心底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:02:01.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}风吹而过 泪水渗眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:08.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}你的身影 已变得更远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.70,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}任何时候都不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:12.87,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}哪怕一切的一切全部改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:15.08,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}不忘记那一件 那一件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.46,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}稀松平常之事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.57,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}终会让你看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:21.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}那被光芒包裹着的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:23.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}守护 守护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:26.89,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\be1}直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================Text===================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君 没忘带什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小汐 来送行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天 有早苗陪着渚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也常去露个脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了汐能平安出生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在尽己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有时在想 早苗会不会恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有遇到我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚就不会经历与危险相伴的生产
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我改变了渚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见她时 她真的看起来非常柔弱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我觉得若不上前搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她便会永远止步于坡道下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直过于自负
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为她是因为与我相遇才变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也随着她而变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实如此啊 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:04:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和秋生 都不知有多感谢朋也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我搞不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在也还会留在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然朋友少些 但也会守着小小的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然 就是遇到了比我好得多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过得比现在更加幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是不可能的哦 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道早苗很善良 一定会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我有点孩子气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我继续工作着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能翱翔天空的机器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作这能将我和她带离这个世界的机器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是你的生日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团子大家族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西再增加下去能怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来也没地方在卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难办吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是办不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 亏你能找得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君费了好大的劲找到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年添一个如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐会变成真的大家族哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的那些会不会妒忌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 一次抱不了三个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 朋也君抱抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有渚的味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 去年四月就这么调侃过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春原同学 新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小渚久违了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不好意思呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思议…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别老是神经大条
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上社会了行动模式还是没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你也没资格说别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 藤林 你们来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也从美国回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家新年快乐的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能摸摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很美好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 下一个是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为虾米啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是智代一家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟也很精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫泽同学也寄来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很融洽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边是仁科和杉坂同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝愿能生个健康宝宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:07:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给芽衣妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳野先生的新曲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过自费出版 又开始搞音乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗贝＆斯帕尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.49,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗贝（Robbe）：澳大利亚的模型生产商 斯帕尼亚（Spanien）：德语，即西班牙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是爱与扳手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.54,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(405,410)}Love
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.54,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(475,410)}Spanner
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是高中毕业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌名不同寻常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是芳野先生和我一起想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实名字已经改得很正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 冈崎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 都叫冈崎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 男的冈崎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么称呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为父亲 是怎样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪的问题啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想听听…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为人父母会是怎样的感觉呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直觉得当父母是很遥远的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:09:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 听说你们要做父母了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就突然又觉得它近在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在你俩面前说不太合适
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得父亲并不是想当就当的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得和地震 落雷之类的天灾是一类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道是怀着怎样的心情去成为父亲的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也行啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我也难说现在自己有没有这种真实感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有了喜欢的人 为了她而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就变这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来冈崎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一点都没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来觉得你和小渚远远离去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实还是近在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我来之前也有点紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得你们俩在人生路上超了我好多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命真是不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪里来 又会向哪里去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 现在在做和爸爸妈妈一样的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于「藏起的世界」…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与这个世界紧密相邻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无法看到或感知的另一个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但出乎意料 事情也不一定就是那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这或许和超维有关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据现有学说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所认知的物质依附于高维世界的膜上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然无法摆脱其存在方式这一界限…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但打个比方 重力能就可以超越时空往返…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.06,0:10:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得简单些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的说明就非常非常简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界和藏起的世界可能是紧密相连的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间 空间及人们的意识不可思议地相互作用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会重塑两个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是创造出新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此这般地相互影响 可能就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这些生灵是否也和那世界有关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有 也可能没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界真的充满了未知
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知被藏起的世界会是怎样的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会突然想起那时的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已终结的世界里的少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会知道那故事呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我想到点事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着那世界里是否也有我们一般的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热闹地生活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏起的世界可能不止一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有学说认为 多种多样的世界平行存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤林 以前你占卜时也这么说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是只有一个固定的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是有着各种可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 说不准…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着这里某位在和我交往的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我是绝对不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会看上你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法创造出什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做的只有堆砌破烂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么努力都是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何时 我停了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.57,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春来了面包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小镇不断改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有事物能不做改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人要生存下去就会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这里对你来说是很重要的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果去妨碍这工程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚会变健康吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里建起大医院 对小镇居民都是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们的感伤所能左右的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得自己要讨厌这小镇了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜托相关人员 保住了几棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿智也干过类似的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿智？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 智代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改成在医院生了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是设施齐全些比较放心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽人事然后什么什么 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会下雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 下起了大雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽车火车无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全镇都像患重病般陷入瘫痪时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚发起高烧 同时开始阵痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分娩提前两星期到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚 振作点 渚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会生下小汐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会和朋也君 和小汐一起生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八木小姐来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车还是动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在这时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古河先生请烧水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量多些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈崎先生请给夫人打气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以握着手的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚 我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别输啊 渚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安地生出来 然后开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和汐一起 开始三人的新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静冷静 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 「呼～」地呼口气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 很好 来 「呼～」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 放松
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚多次昏了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又被疼醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这残忍的情形 让人目不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这漫长…看不到终点的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎会永无止境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也意识模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为心已承受不住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为对一切都绝望了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也…君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听见吧 我们的孩子的哭声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最先抱着的是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是汐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小汐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女孩…很精神的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在家里生下来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然让小汐受了不少苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好…真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…有点累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我…稍稍休息一下吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 医生还没来么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在来不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚 等等啊 渚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再…多说说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要听着就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 是我们的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长得像小猴一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫她试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:18:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸哦 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是妈妈 看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被无视了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定很快就会长大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进小学 然后我和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去公开课 运动会之类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全家一起参加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是最不把那些当回事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 汐的脸蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过会一直陪在我身旁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过会永远在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数次…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数次地做过这样的约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是认为人活着碰不到好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也压根不好玩的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易追寻到的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 渚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这所学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一切的一切 都无法不做改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快开心的事 都无法永远持续
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.41,0:21:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 还会继续喜欢这个地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.36,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有相遇就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样踏上不同的路途就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会和渚交往 不会和她结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…也不会有汐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样 就不会生出这种哀痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有相遇…就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================ED===================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:26.07,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}双眼凝视着 流动的云朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:32.99,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}心中感受着 天空变幻的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:41.18,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}伫立不前的我们 察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.32,0:22:48.20,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}这变迁的世界编织出的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:55.44,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}伸出的指尖 不断寻找着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:23:04.13,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那恒久不变的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.35,0:23:11.69,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}举起的手中火炬闪亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:19.42,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那是通向明天的小小路标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:26.75,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}现在也在不断回响
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:34.28,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那一天的话语 终将化为誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:39.04,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)}推动我前行
